e utslippene globalt, vil de norske utslippene isolert sett synke.", "(\u00a9NTB)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "eecb61deee1856f70e1ce4347e4d1a281789455f441d6c187ef2dc4858f7ae87"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-07T13:18:40.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Regjeringens varslede bruk av mer \"konvensjonelt\" biodrivstoff i Norge vil \u00f8ke verdens klimautslipp med flere titusen tonn CO2, if\u00f8lge en ny SSB-rapport."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/d578e30264c5834b4c61851073469346d3973c49.jpg?58beea18"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "256x256"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "SSB: Biodrivstoff-satsing \u00f8ker klimautslippene -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "d578e30264c5834b4c61851073469346d3973c49"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["\u00f8ke", "utslipp", "drivstoff", "globale", "globale utslipp", "biodrivstoff", "bruk", "konvensjonelt", "konvensjonelt biodrivstoff"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["bjart holtsmark", "aftenposten", "venstre"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["europa", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "vidar helgesen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/innenriks"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://static.polarismedia.no/skins/prod/publication/adressa/gfx/applefavicon.png"}, {"field": "o